<P><FONT SIZE=2><A NAME="FN14" HREF="#TXT14">14</A></FONT> Donn Downey, <CITE>Toronto Globe and Mail,</CITE> Oct. 28; Manuel Torres Calderon, <CITE>Excelsior</CITE> (Mexico City), Oct. 7; COHA's <CITE>Washington Report on the Hemisphere,</CITE> Oct. 28; <CITE>Latinamerica Press</CITE> (Peru), Oct. 29; <CITE>Excelsior,</CITE> Nov. 4, 1987.

