<P><FONT SIZE=2><A NAME="FN3" HREF="#TXT3">3</A></FONT> Gwen Ifill, <CITE>NYT;</CITE> John Aloysius Farrell, <CITE>Boston Globe,</CITE> Nov 8, 1993. Lewis, Nov. 5, 1993. Richard Berke, "Rescuing a Lawmaker From Labor's Revenge," <CITE>NYT,</CITE> March 15, 1994.

