<P><FONT SIZE=2><A NAME="FN8" HREF="#TXT8">8</A></FONT> <CITE>Guardian,</CITE> May 24, 1994.

<P><FONT SIZE=2><A NAME="FN9" HREF="#TXT9">9</A></FONT> <CITE>Vancouver Sun,</CITE> March 7; <CITE>Third World Resurgence,</CITE> No. 44; <CITE>Financial Times,</CITE> June 8, 1994.

