<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>
MADNESS: Feedback Page
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<FRAMESET ROWS="6, *">

<NOFRAMES>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../plugtile.gif" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#0000FF"><BASEFONT SIZE=4>
<TT><B>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="feedback.gif"><P>
<FONT SIZE=+1>MADNESS Contributors' Guidelines</CENTER></FONT>
<P>
<BLOCKQUOTE><BLOCKQUOTE><FONT SIZE=+1>So you want to contribute or give feedback?  EXCELLENT.  MADNESS welcomes any type of suggestion or contribution, from the downright stupid to the upright brilliant.  Before you put the proverbial quill to the proverbial parchment, there are a couple things you should consider:</FONT></BLOCKQUOTE></BLOCKQUOTE>
<OL>
<LI><FONT SIZE=+2>U</FONT>nless you specify otherwise, all submissions and suggestions may be made public.  If you want to send private e-mail or suggestions, just put somewhere in the message that it's not for public consumption.
<P>
<LI><FONT SIZE=+2>I</FONT>f you are making suggestions for next week's installment or tossing some ideas for plot or character development your message may be any length.  If you are making SUBMISSIONS, however (i.e. word-for-word character suggestions, lists of character traits, background anecdotes--anything you'd like to be printed AS-IS), please keep it short--500 words or so is good for a top limit.  Remember: <FONT SIZE=+1>I have the right to edit everything.</FONT> I'll run any changes by you so that you can okay them before your piece goes up.
<P> 
<LI><FONT SIZE=+2>K</FONT>eep the submissions reasonable if you can.  I like a alien abduction or group sex story as much as the next guy, but unless the plot calls for it (and hey, it might) try not to get too weird.
<P>
<LI><FONT SIZE=+2>E</FONT>verything that you submit becomes property of MADNESS. 
<P>
<LI><FONT SIZE=+2>O</FONT>ther than that, anything goes as long as it makes sense.  
</OL>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=+2>
<CENTER>SEND IT TO:<BR><A HREF="mailto: jay@user1.channel1.com">jay@user1.channel1.com</CENTER></A></FONT>
<BR>
<BR>
<CENTER>
<A HREF="../index.htm" TARGET="_top"><IMG SRC="../madnessh.gif" BORDER=0><BR>to contents</A><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>(or pull down top frame)</FONT></CENTER>
<BR><BR>
<HR NOSHADE>
<FONT SIZE=-2>(c) All material copyright Jay Sand. <A HREF="mailto: jay@user1.channel1.com">jay@user1.channel1.com</A> Of course you may use what you want, just tell me first.</FONT>
</BODY>
