<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>
Madness Overview
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<FRAMESET ROWS="6,*"
<NOFRAMES>
<BODY BACKGROUND="plugtile.gif" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#FF0000" VLINK="#FF0000"><P>
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="madblu.gif">
<CENTER>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=+2>
MADNESS is the Web's premier<BR>
work of collaborative, episodic,
hypertext fiction.  Tune in every week to<BR>
follow our protagonists:</FONT></BLOCKQUOTE></CENTER>
<BLOCKQUOTE><BLOCKQUOTE>
<UL>
<LI><FONT SIZE=+5>L</FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>ucas Wood, our guitar toting, self-doubting, diary-writing, politically curious aspiring world-changer,</FONT>
<P> 
<LI><FONT SIZE=+5>W</FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>atson Clubbard, our socially inept eccentric Wall Street whiz, and</FONT>
<P>
<LI><FONT SIZE=+5>A</FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>nna Christiana, our assertive, opinionated, sexually adventurous daughter of a washed-up '70s sit-com star</FONT>
<P>
</UL>
<FONT SIZE=+2>as they fumble through life and love in the warped, wild and often wacky wilderness of the city that can kick your city's ass.</FONT>
<P>
<STRONG>If this is this is your first visit . . . :
<OL>
<LI>Check out this week's installment first to get the gist of the story,
<LI>Cruise through the past weeks' installments to get even more gist, and
<LI>Once you're fully gisted, dig into the pounds and pound of character background and explore "the fireside."
</OL></STRONG>
<FONT SIZE=+1>Feel free to <A HREF="feedback/index.htm" TARGET="_top">
suggest characters, information and plot twists at every turn!
</A></FONT>.
<P>
And now . . . to<BR>
<A HREF="index.htm" TARGET="_top"><IMG SRC="madgrn.gif" BORDER=0></A></BLOCKQUOTE></BLOCKQUOTE></TT></B>
<BR>
</BODY>

