<hr>
<h3>Commercial Database Vendors</h3>
<h4><a href="http://www.cas.org"><IMG src="/images/WORLD.GIF" border=0></a> <a href="http://www.cas.org">
Chemical Abstracts Service</a></h4>            
CAS (Chemical Abstracts Service), a division of the American Chemical Society, provides a broad range of scientific information products, from
focused topical publications to comprehensive online sources. 

<h4><a href="http://www.dialog.com"><IMG src="/images/WORLD.GIF" border=0></a> <a href="http://www.dialog.com">DataStar</a></h4>
The DataStar Information Retrieval Service has over 400 databases from a
broad scope of disciplines. DataStar shines with its unique collection of
European information, newspapers and newswires. 

<h4><a href="http://www.dialog.com"><IMG src="/images/WORLD.GIF" border=0></a> <a href="http://www.dialog.com">DIALOG</a></h4>
DIALOG is a Knight-Ridder Information, Inc. service that provides access to
over 450 online databases.



