<dt><a href=http://www.pennwell.com/ogj.html>Oil & Gas 
Journal</a><dd>International petroleum news and technology.  Additionally 
offers links to other petroleum industry publications like Russian Oil & Gas 
Guide, Ocean Oil Weekly Report, The Oilman Weekly Newsletter, and 
Asia/Pacific Oil Weekly Report. 

<dt><a href="http://www.thomson.com:8866/oq.html">Optical and Quantum 
Electronics</a> <dd>A trial subscription with abstracts only.

<dt><a href="http://www.c3.lanl.gov:8078/">Physical Review A, B, C, D, and 
E</a><dd>Covers 1989-1994. Access restricted to LANL staff.

<dt><a href="http://publish.aps.org/PRBO/prbohome.html">Physical Review B - 
Rapid Communications Online</a><dd>Access restricted to individual 
subscribing members.

<dt><a href="http://ojps.aip.org/prco/">Physical Review C</a><dd>Holdings:  
vol. 53, no. 2 (Feb. 1996)-    .  <a href="http://lib-
www.lanl.gov/lanlonly/password.htm#physrevc">Password</a>

<dt><a href="http://publish.aps.org/PRDO/">Physical Review D</a><dd>Holdings: 
vol. 54, no. 1 (July 1, 1996)-   .  Access restricted to LANL staff.

<dt><a href="http://ojps.aip.org/prlo/">Physical 
Review Letters online</a><dd>Access restricted to LANL staff. 

<dt><a href="http://www.iop.org/EJ/3/39/bin/journal/pb">Physics in Medicine and 
Biology</a><dd>Access restricted to LANL staff.  

<dt><a href="http://www.iop.org/EJ/3/39/bin/journal/pp">Plasma Physics and 
ControlledFusion</a><dd>Access restricted to LANL staff.  

<dt><a href="http://www.iop.org/EJ/3/39/bin/journal/ps">Plasma Sources 
Science andTechnology</a><dd>Access restricted to LANL staff.  

<dt><a href="http://www.idealibrary.com/login.html">Plasmid</a><dd>Holdings:  
vol. 34, no. 2 (1995)-   . Access restricted to LANL staff.  <a href="http://lib-
www.lanl.gov/lanlonly/password.htm#applas">Password</a>

<dt><a href="http://www.ams.org/proc/">Proceedings of the American 
Mathematical Society</a>  

<dt><a href="http://journals.at-home.com/PNAS">Proceedings of the National 
Academy of Sciences</a><dd>Tables of contents and abstracts beginning with 
v.93, Jan. 1996.

<dt><a href="http://www.prosci.uci.edu/index.shtml">Protein 
Science</a><dd>Tables of contents and abstracts beginning with v.5 #11, Nov. 
1996.
<dt><a href="#Top"><i>(top of page)</i></a></dt>
<hr>

<a name="Q-S"><h3>Q-S</h3></a>

<dt><a href="http://www.idealibrary.com/login.html">Quaternary 
Research</a><dd>Holdings:  vol. 45, no. 1 (1996)-   . Access restricted to LANL 
staff.  <a href="http://lib-
www.lanl.gov/lanlonly/password.htm#apquat">Password</a>

<dt><a href="http://www.iop.org/EJ/3/39/bin/journal/rp">Reports on Progress in 
Physics</a><dd>Access restricted to LANL staff.  

<dt><a href="http://science-
mag.aaas.org/science/">Science</a><dd>Summaries/abstracts of items in 
Science since October 1995 with full text of This Week in Science: Research 
Highlights.  Contents only for June 30-September 29, 1995. 

<dt><a href="http://165.123.33.33/toc.html">The Scientist</a><br>  

<dt><a href="http://www.iop.org/EJ/3/39/bin/journal/ss">Semiconductor Science 
andTechnology</a><dd>Access restricted to LANL staff.  

<dt><a href="http://cartan.u-strasbg.fr:80/~slc/index.html">Seminaire 
Lotharingien de Combinatoire</a>

<dt><a href="http://www.emis.de/journals/SWJPAM/index.html">  The Southwest 
Journal of Pure and Applied Mathematics</a>

<dt><a href="http://www.iop.org/EJ/3/39/bin/journal/su">Superconductor Science 
andTechnology</a><dd>Access restricted to LANL staff.  

<dt><a href="http://www.idealibrary.com/login.html">Superlattices and 
Microstructures</a><dd>Holdings:  vol. 19, no. 1 (1996)-   . Access restricted to 
LANL staff.  <a href="http://lib-
www.lanl.gov/lanlonly/password.htm#apsuper">Password</a>
