through Jan. 4, 1993.)

 <dt><a href="http://www.usnews.com/usnews/main.htm">U.S. News & World 
Report</a><dd>Online version with top stories, etc.  Also includes the annual <a 
href="http://www.usnews.com/usnews/fair/home.htm">College Fair</a> with 
college rankings.  

