<dt><a href="http://www.eurekalert.org">EurekAlert!</a> 
<dd>Daily science and technology news produced by the American Association for the Advancement of Science.
<dt><a href="http://www.ft.com">Financial Times (London)</a>
<dd>Free access, but registration required.
<dt><a href="http://webvisions.com.sg/inkpot/news">Flying Inkpot's World Newspaper Links</a>
<dd>Links to newspapers around the world.
<dt><a href="http://www.insidechina.com">Inside China Today</a>
<dt><a href="http://www.latimes.com/HOME">Los Angeles Times</a>
<dd>Free access, but registration required.
<dt><a href="http://www.nytimes.com">New York Times</a>
<dd>Free access, but registration required.
<dt><a href="http://www.newspapers.com/npcom1.htm">Newspapers within the United States</a>
<dd>List of newspapers by state.
<dt><a href="http://pathfinder.com"> Pathfinder's News Now</a>
<dd>Includes news feeds from News  Reuters, Time-Warner, Sports Ticker and Quote.Com
<dt><a href="http://www.rcnews.com">Royal City News</a>
<dd>Monthly magazine from Santa Fe.
<dt><a href="http://www.russiatoday.com">Russia Today</a>
<dt><a href="http://pathfinder.com/@@ZCd8qAYA0uxkHIjY/time/daily/">Time News Service Daily</a>
<dt><a href="http://www.the-times.co.uk">The Times (London)</a>  
<dd>Free access, but registration required.
<dt><a href="http://www.usatoday.com">USA Today</a>
<dt><a href="http://www.usnews.com/usnews/main.htm">U.S. News & World Report</a>
<dt><a href="http://unisci.com">UniSci</a>
<dd>Research News From American Universities
