<head><title>LANL Research Library: New Items</title>  
</head><body bgcolor="#ffffff"><img src="/images/cic14.gif" alt="Los Alamos National Laboratory Research Library">    

 <h1>New Items</h1>      

<hr>
January 10, 1997
<ul>
<li><b>Engineering Resources Page:</b> A link has been added to the 
<a href="http://patent.womplex.ibm.com/">IBM Patent Server</a> which 
contains descriptions of patents from 1971 and images for the 
patents issued in the last ten years.
</ul>
January 9, 1997
<ul>
<li><b>Hot Topics and News Page:</b>Link has been added to <a href="http://search.nytimes.com/web/docsroot/yr/mo/day/early/us-nuke-update.html">
Nuclear Arms Builders Move From Creators to Custodians</a>
a special article from the <i>New York Times</i>, Jan. 6, 1997.
January 7, 1997
<ul>
<li><b>Hot Topics and News Page:</b> Links have been added to pages featuring <a href="http://lib-www.lanl.gov/infores/hot/halebopp.htm">Comet Hale-Bopp</a>.
<li><b>Computer Science Resources Page:</b> Links have been added to the 
<a href="http://matrix.psych.ualberta.ca/~mike/Pearl_Street/Dictionary/dictionary.html">
Cognitive Science Dictionary</a>, <a href="http://www.tu-graz.ac.at/Cjargon">
Hacker's jargon</a>, and <a href="http://www.msg.net/kadow/answers.html">
Kadow's Internet Dictionary</a>.
<li><b>Mathematics Resources Page:</b> Links have been added to the 
<a href="http://www-math.cudenver.edu/~hgreenbe/glossary/glossary.html">
Mathematical Programming Glossary</a> and 
<a href="http://www.maths.uq.edu.au/~pkp/probweb/probweb.html">
The Probability Web</a>.
<li><b>Physics Resources Page:</b> Links have been added to  
<a href="http://www.caretaker.com/">Radioactivity & Radiochemistry</a> and to the 
tables of contents of <a href="http://wwwsoc.nacsis.ac.jp/jjap/index.html">
Japanese Journal of Applied Physics</a>, 
<a href="http://wwwsoc.nacsis.ac.jp/jps/jpsj/index.html">
Journal of the Physical Society of Japan</a>, 
<a href="http://www.vchgroup.de/akademie-verlag/office/pss/">
Physica Status Solidi a and b</a>, 
<a href="http://www.aip.org/journals/phf/phf.html">Physics of Fluids</a>, 
<a href="http://science.springer.de/zphys-a/">
Zeitschrift fr Physik A - Hadrons and Nuclei</a>, 
<a href="http://science.springer.de/zphys-b/">
Zeitschrift fr Physik B - Condensed Matter</a>, 
<a href="http://science.springer.de/zphys-c/">
Zeitschrift fr Physik C - Particles and Fields</a>, and 
<a href="http://science.springer.de/zphys-d/">
Zeitschrift fr Physik D - Atoms, Molecules and Clusters</a>.
</ul>

January 3, 1997
<ul>

<li><b>Engineering Resources Page:</b> A link has been added to the tables of contents for 
journals published by <a href="http://www.thomson.com:8866/chaphall/default.html">
Chapman & Hall</a>. 
<li><b>Physics Resources Page:</b> Links have been added to the journal 
<a href="http://www.icmp.lviv.ua/ICMP/JOURNAL/index.shtml">Condensed Matter Physics</a>, 
and to tables of contents for <a href="http://www.thomson.com:8866/chaphall/default.html">
Chapman & Hall</a>, <a href="http://www.elsevier.nl/inca/">
Elsevier Science Titles</a>, <a href="http://www.wwilkins.com/health_physics/">
Health Physics</a>, <a href="http://www.aip.org/journals/jcp/jcp.html">
Journal of Chemical Physics</a>, <a href="http://www.phy.duke.edu/~hm/JLTP/index.html">
Journal of Low Temperature Physics</a>, and 
<a href="http://www.aip.org/journals/jmp/jmp.html">Journal of Mathematical Physics</a>.
</ul>
January 2, 1997
<ul>
<li><b>Engineering Resources Page:</b> Links have been added to the 
<a href="http://www.ascepub.infor.com:8601/pubshome.html">
American Society of Civil Engineers Publications</a> - current issues only and to 
<A HREF="http://www.iee.org.uk/publish/journals/profjrnl/ieeproc.html" >
IEE Proceedings Tables of Contents</A>.
<li><b>Physics Resources Page:</b> Links have been added to the tables of 
contents for <a href="http://info.ifpan.edu.pl/ACTA/acta.home.html">
Acta physica Polonica A</a>, <a href="http://www.amherst.edu/~ajp/">
